Proposed operations policies:

1. The foundation only links to websites on Mastercoin Foundation web assets when the administrator of the URL is a foundation staff or board member or service provider, when the owner of the website is a member of the Mastercoin Foundation, or when the link refers to to media and press pertaining to Mastercoin Foundation.  In the case of online communities and forums, the community or forum has at least one administrative member who is also a staff member, board member or service provider to the Mastercoin Foundation.
